# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
# Scratch/cache dirs test build-shelling gates create at repo root (light-dark-minify.test.ts's
# dist-tkt0002-gate-scratch, theme-provider-build-fixture.test.ts's dist-theme-provider-gate-scratch, and
# build-css.ts's dist-shared-build-cache) — each is try/finally-cleaned in the normal case, but a wildcard
# closes the gap for an interrupted run (a crashed process, Ctrl-C mid-test) rather than relying on that alone.
dist-*
*.local

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

# reference dumps (design-token exports, etc.) — not source of truth, not committed
.claude/docs/other
.claude/docs/brand
.env

# Vitest browser-mode run artifacts (Playwright screenshots/attachments) — on-failure debris only.
# ADR-0110: `__baselines__/` (committed visual-regression reference PNGs) is DELIBERATELY NOT listed
# here and must stay tracked — do not add a blanket `__baselines__` ignore.
.vitest-attachments/
**/__screenshots__/